From: Felipe <fel.c18@gmail.com>
Date: 2026-05-16
Subject: meson: remove -Werror=override-init (GCC 15 breaks errno-to-name.h)

GCC 15 valida designated initializer overrides mais agressivamente.
errno-to-name.h (auto-gerado) tem aliases (EAGAIN/EWOULDBLOCK,
EDEADLK/EDEADLOCK, ENOTSUP/EOPNOTSUPP) que disparam -Werror=override-init.

Downgrade pra warning (sem o Werror prefix).

--- a/meson.build
+++ b/meson.build
@@ -346,7 +346,7 @@
         '-Werror=missing-declarations',
         '-Werror=missing-prototypes',
         '-Werror=overflow',
-        '-Werror=override-init',
+        '-Woverride-init',
         '-Werror=return-type',
         '-Werror=shift-count-overflow',
         '-Werror=shift-overflow=2',
